title: 132-Pound Woman Bench Presses 325 Pounds, Entire Football Team Goes Nuts
text:

Let’s give it up for Thompson: When she isn’t busy being a mom or teaching a high school math class, the 43-year-old spends her time breaking weightlifting records at powerlifting competitions. She stands at 5’5” and competes in the 138-pound weight class, so naturally, she was probably pretty stoked to show up a bunch of beefy college football players. And judging by their raucous applause in the clip, they were also pretty hyped to witness Thompson’s fitness feat. Only a couple members of Liberty’s football squad weigh more than 325 pounds, meaning Thompson could probably bench most of the guys in that weight room.
